snippet.title: Tobe & Fat Nwigwe: Why Black Women Will Always Be An After Thought
snippet.description:
In this video, Cynthia G  reacts to a viral video clip of rapper Tobe Nwigwe and his wife Fat, and explains why black women will always be an after thought
